      "title": "Background",
      "text": "'Scream a little louder, or I'll keep you trapped in my mantle forever.'\n\nFor most of the Bloodborn, Sirene's name had long sunk into the depths of forgotten memory, fading with each passing generation.\n\nBut the moment the silver-haired sinner stepped through the gates of Bathory Castle, a few idle murmurs from deep within stirred—enough to make her insolent descendants recall the fear etched into their blood.",
